{
  "texts": [
    "• We construct a novel meta-toxic knowledge graph.",
    "To our best knowledge, it is the first domain-specific knowledge graph for hate and toxic speech detection.",
    "We will open-source the knowledge graph upon paper acceptance.",
    "MetaTox for hate and toxic speech detection.",
    "In particular, MetaTox addresses the notorious false positive misjudgment issue, decreasing the ethical risk of hurting the freedom of speech."
  ]
}